export const initialReservations = [
  {
    id: '1',
    user: 'Juan Pérez',
    room: 'Sala A',
    startTime: new Date('2024-10-15T10:00:00'),
    endTime: new Date('2024-10-15T11:00:00'),
    title: 'Reunión equipo',
    description: 'Discusión semanal',
    status: 'confirmed'
  },
  {
    id: '2',
    user: 'Ana García',
    room: 'Sala B',
    startTime: new Date('2024-10-16T14:00:00'),
    endTime: new Date('2024-10-16T15:30:00'),
    title: 'Presentación',
    description: 'Demo del proyecto',
    status: 'pending'
  },
  {
    id: '3',
    user: 'Carlos López',
    room: 'Sala A',
    startTime: new Date('2024-10-17T09:00:00'),
    endTime: new Date('2024-10-17T10:30:00'),
    title: 'Entrevista',
    description: 'Candidato nuevo',
    status: 'confirmed'
  }
];

export const generateId = () => Date.now().toString(36) + Math.random().toString(36).substr(2);
